<!-- Blog Area -->
<div class="recent-job-area-two pt-100 pb-70">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <h2>From Our last editions</h2>
                    <div class="bar"></div>
                    <p>After a successful experience in Ghana, we were empowered by our mentors and peers at CRI-Paris to continue our educational efforts. Furthermore, we were able to put out together our specializations around the implementation of digital and frugal technologies for sustainable solutions.</p>
                    <p>Therefore, over the course of the 2019-2020 academic year we focused on the development of project-based activities to create a summer school for students with the goal of developing new skills.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="browse-btn float-end">
                    <a href="{{ path('all_editions') }}"> Browse More Editions <i class="ri-arrow-right-s-line"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row pt-45 justify-content-center">
            {% for edition in editions %}
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-img">
                        <a href="blog-details.html">
                            {% if edition.avatar %}
                                {% for photo in edition.avatar %}
                                    <a href="">
                                        <img src="{{ asset('uploads/' ~ photo.nom) }}" alt="{{ photo.nom }}">
                                    </a>
                                {% endfor %}
                            {% endif %}
                        </a>
                        <a href="tags.html" class="tag" target="_blank">
                            Job Board
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <i class="ri-time-line"></i> June 14, 2021
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="ri-mail-line"></i> 02 Comments
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <h3><a href="{{ path('edition_show', {'slug': edition.slug}) }}">{{ edition.nom }}</a></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Blog Area End -->